quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  36,33,"“Ndipo chisonyezo chawo ndi nthaka yakufa; timaiukitsa (ndi madzi) ndi kutulutsa m’menemo njere, zomwe zina mwa izo amadya"
  36,34,“Ndipo tapanga m’menemo minda ya kanjedza ndi mphesa; ndipo tatulutsa m’menemo akasupe
  36,35,“Kuti azidya zipatso zake pomwe sizidapangidwe ndi manja awo. Kodi bwanji sathokoza (Allah)
  36,36,"“Alemekezeke (Allah), Amene adalenga zinthu zonse, chachimuna ndi chachikazi, kuchokera m’zimene nthaka ikutulutsa, ndi iwo omwe ndi zina zimene (anthu) sakudziwa"
  36,37,"“Ndiponso chisonyezo chawo ndiusiku. M’menemo timachotsamo usana (womwe umabisa usiku), ndipo (anthu) amangozindikira ali mu mdima"
  36,38,"“۞ Ndipo dzuwa; limayenda m’njira ndi m’nthawi yake imene idakonzedwa kwa ilo. Chikonzero chimenecho ncha (Allah) Wamphamvu zoposa, Wodziwa kwambiri"
  36,39,"“Ndiponso mwezi; tidaukonzera malo oimirapo mpaka kukafika pomwe umabwerera ndi kukhala wochepa ndi wokhota monga nthambi ya mtengo wa kanjedza, youma komanso yokhota"
  36,40,"“Nkosatheka kwa dzuwa kukumana ndi mwezi (njira yake); nawonso usiku sungathe kupambana usana (pakudza nthawi yausana isadathe, koma zimasinthana). Ndipo chilichonse mwa izo chimasambira m’njira yake (imene Allah adachikonzera)"
  36,41,“Ndiponso pali chisonyezo kwa iwo (chosonyeza madalitso Athu pa iwo). Ndithu tidaukweza mtundu wawo mchombo chodzazidwa (ndi zonse zamoyo)
  36,42,“Ndipo tidawapangira chonga icho chomwe akuchikwera
  36,43,"“Ndipo ngati titafuna tikhoza kuwamiza m’madzi, ndipo sangapezeke wowathandiza, ndiponso sangapulumutsidwe"
  36,44,“Koma (sitikuwamiza) chifukwa cha chifundo Chathu pa iwo ndi kuti asangalale kufikira nthawi yawo (yofera)
  36,45,"“Ndipo kukanenedwa kwa iwo: “Opani zomwe ziri patsogolo panu ndi zomwe ziri pambuyo panu kuti muchitiridwe chifundo.” (Iwo akunyoza malangizowo)"
  36,46,“Ndipo palibe chisonyezo chilichonse mwa zisonyezo za Mbuye wawo (zosonyeza umodzi Wake ndi kukhoza Kwake) chomwe chidawadzera popanda kuchinyoza (ndi kuchikana)
  36,47,"“Ndipo kukanenedwa kwa iwo: “Patsani (amphawi) zimene Allah wakupatsani.” Osakhulupirira amanena kwa okhulupirira: “Kodi tidyetse yemwe Allah akadafuna akadamdyetsa; (titsutsane ndi cholinga cha Allah)? Ndithu inu simuli kanthu koma muli m’kusokera koonekeratu.”"
  36,48,"“Ndipo akunena (mwachipongwe kwa okhulupirira): “Kodi lonjezo ili (lakudza kwa chiweruziro), lidzachitika liti, ngati mukunena zoona?”"
  36,49,"“Palibe chimene akuyembekeza, koma ndi mkuwe umodzi womwe udzawamaliza mwadzidzidzi uku iwo akukangana"
  36,50,"“Ndipo sangathe kuuza wina mawu pa chinthu, ndiponso sangathe kubwerera ku maanja awo"